GO AHEAD. TAKE THEM.

230
00:10:32,725 --> 00:10:37,293
BUT I'M WARNING YOU --
IT'S EITHER THE PILLS OR ME.

231
00:10:45,859 --> 00:10:48,859
Teacher: OKAY, EVERYBODY.
BACK TO WORK. BACK TO WORK.

232
00:10:48,892 --> 00:10:50,226
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

233
00:10:55,359 --> 00:10:57,359
HELLO?

234
00:10:57,393 --> 00:11:00,393
HEY.
GREAT TEST SHOT.

235
00:11:01,725 --> 00:11:04,126
SO, YOU READY
TO BE IN <i>MAXIM?</i>

236
00:11:04,159 --> 00:11:05,859
DEFINITELY.

237
00:11:07,592 --> 00:11:10,093
* IT'S IN THE WATER, BABY 

238
00:11:10,126 --> 00:11:12,493
* IT'S IN THE PILLS
THAT BRING YOU DOWN *

239
00:11:12,526 --> 00:11:15,026
* IT'S IN THE WATER, BABY 

240
00:11:15,059 --> 00:11:17,625
* IT'S IN YOUR BAG
OF GOLDEN BROWN *

241
00:11:17,659 --> 00:11:19,959
* IT'S IN THE WATER, BABY 

242
00:11:19,992 --> 00:11:22,625
* IT'S IN YOUR FREQUENCY 

243
00:11:22,659 --> 00:11:25,259
* IT'S IN THE WATER, BABY 

244
00:11:25,293 --> 00:11:28,792
* IT'S BETWEEN YOU AND ME 

245
00:11:37,293 --> 00:11:39,625
* IT'S IN THE WATER, BABY 

246
00:11:39,659 --> 00:11:42,226
* IT'S IN YOUR FAMILY TREE 

247
00:11:42,259 --> 00:11:44,792
* IT'S IN THE WATER, BABY 

248
00:11:44,826 --> 00:11:47,560
* IT'S BETWEEN YOU AND ME 

249
00:11:47,592 --> 00:11:51,026
* BITE THE HAND THAT FEEDS 

250
00:11:52,359 --> 00:11:57,093
* TAP THE VEIN THAT BLEEDS 

251
00:11:57,126 --> 00:12:00,725
* I'D BREAK THE BACK OF LOVE
FOR YOU *

252
00:12:00,759 --> 00:12:02,426
[ HORN BLARES ]

253
00:12:02,460 --> 00:12:04,560
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

254
00:12:08,992 --> 00:12:10,826
NATHAN.

255
00:12:10,859 --> 00:12:12,193
GOD!

256
00:12:12,226 --> 00:12:13,526
WHAT HAPPENED?

257
00:12:13,560 --> 00:12:15,126
IT'S OKAY.
DON'T WORRY.

258
00:12:15,159 --> 00:12:17,226
THESE DAYS THEY CAN
GRAFT SKIN FROM MY ASS.

259
00:12:17,259 --> 00:12:18,759
ARE YOU HURT ANYWHERE ELSE?

260
00:12:18,792 --> 00:12:19,892
NO, I'M FINE.

261
00:12:19,926 --> 00:12:21,393
BIKE'S PRETTY MESSED UP,
THOUGH.

262
00:12:21,426 --> 00:12:22,659
BIKE, GREAT.

263
00:12:22,692 --> 00:12:27,093
OKAY, I WANT YOU TO GET THE CAR
BACK AS SOON AS YOU CAN

264
00:12:27,126 --> 00:12:29,093
BECAUSE I NEED YOU
ON THIS PLANET.

265
00:12:29,126 --> 00:12:31,026
HALEY, NOTHING'S
GOING TO HAPPEN TO ME.

266
00:12:31,059 --> 00:12:34,592
YOU ARE NOT INVINCIBLE.

267
00:12:34,625 --> 00:12:36,959
NATHAN...

268
00:12:36,992 --> 00:12:39,526
I KNOW THAT IT'S REALLY HARD
FOR YOU TO EXPLAIN

269
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:42,826
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU
DOWN UNDER THAT WATER...

270
00:12:42,859 --> 00:12:44,725
MAYBE KEITH DID SAVE YOU.

271
00:12:44,759 --> 00:12:46,892
MAYBE YOU SAVED YOURSELF.
I DON'T KNOW.

272
00:12:46,926 --> 00:12:49,059
BUT THE POINT IS,
THAT EITHER WAY,

273
00:12:49,093 --> 00:12:52,725
IT MEANS THAT YOU ARE
SUPPOSED TO BE HERE RIGHT NOW.

274
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:54,692
HALES, THAT'S NOT IT.

275
00:12:54,725 --> 00:12:56,992
MY MOM
CAME INTO SCHOOL TODAY,

276
00:12:57,026 --> 00:13:02,293
AND IN FRONT OF EVERYBODY,
CHOSE PILLS OVER ME.

277
00:13:02,326 --> 00:13:04,659
[ SIGHS ]

278
00:13:04,692 --> 00:13:06,725
HERE.

279
00:13:06,759 --> 00:13:08,892
WHERE YOU GOING?

280
00:13:08,926 --> 00:13:11,426
YOU TAKE CARE
OF THE BIKE, PLEASE.

281
00:13:11,460 --> 00:13:14,560
I WILL TAKE CARE
OF YOUR MOTHER.

282
00:13:14,592 --> 00:13:16,093
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

283
00:13:16,126 --> 00:13:17,293
[ SIGHS ]

284
00:13:21,359 --> 00:13:22,892
STAY AWAY FROM HIM.

285
00:13:22,926 --> 00:13:24,892
FOR ALL I CARE,
YOU CAN GO TO HELL,

286
00:13:24,926 --> 00:13:26,892
BUT I WILL NOT LET YOU
TAKE NATHAN WITH YOU.

287
00:13:26,926 --> 00:13:29,393
TALK TO ME IN A FEW YEARS,
HALEY...

288
00:13:29,426 --> 00:13:33,725
WHEN YOUR DREAMS ARE DEAD
AND YOUR CHILD BETRAYS YOU.

289
00:13:33,759 --> 00:13:35,592
THEN WE'LL SEE WHAT KIND
OF MOTHER YOU'LL BE.

290
00:13:35,625 --> 00:13:36,892
NO, NO, NO.

291
00:13:36,926 --> 00:13:40,359
I WILL NEVER EVER
BE LIKE YOU, DEB.

292
00:13:40,393 --> 00:13:43,359
YOU KNOW, PRETTY SOON
NATHAN'S GOING TO REALIZE

293
00:13:43,393 --> 00:13:45,259
THAT PLAYING
COLLEGE BASKETBALL'S

294
00:13:45,293 --> 00:13:48,293
A LOT MORE FUN
THAN PLAYING HOUSE.

295
00:13:48,326 --> 00:13:51,193
I'LL SAVE YOU SOME PILLS.

296
00:13:51,226 --> 00:13:53,226
WHO ARE YOU KIDDING, DEB?

297
00:13:53,259 --> 00:13:55,493
JUNKIES DON'T SAVE PILLS.

298
00:14:03,495 --> 00:14:08,132
[ SIGHS ]
WHAT DO YOU WANT, SHELLY?

299
00:14:08,133 --> 00:14:09,565
I WANT TO APOLOGIZE.

300
00:14:09,599 --> 00:14:11,799
I CAME ON A LITTLE
STRONG EARLIER,

301
00:14:11,832 --> 00:14:14,766
AND I REALIZED CLEAN TEENS
ISN'T FOR EVERYONE.

302
00:14:14,799 --> 00:14:17,233
SO YOU'RE REALLY
NEVER GOING TO HAVE SEX?

303
00:14:17,265 --> 00:14:18,699
NOT UNTIL MY WEDDING NIGHT.

304
00:14:18,732 --> 00:14:20,398
WHY WOULD A GUY
BUY THE COW

305
00:14:20,432 --> 00:14:22,565
WHEN HE CAN GET
THE MILK FOR FREE?

306
00:14:22,599 --> 00:14:25,166
OKAY, DO YOU REALIZE THAT
YOU JUST LIKENED YOURSELF

307
00:14:25,199 --> 00:14:26,632
TO A FARM ANIMAL,

308
00:14:26,665 --> 00:14:28,966
ONE THAT IS FOR SALE,
NO LESS?

309
00:14:28,999 --> 00:14:30,565
IT'S NOT JUST ABOUT THAT.

310
00:14:30,599 --> 00:14:33,966
IT'S ABOUT KEEPING
OUR BODIES PURE.

311
00:14:33,999 --> 00:14:36,999
HAVE YOU EVER HAD CHLAMYDIA
OR GONORRHEA?

312
00:14:37,032 --> 00:14:38,632
NOT FUN.

313
00:14:38,665 --> 00:14:40,699
UH, BURN ME AT THE STAKE,

314
00:14:40,732 --> 00:14:43,799
BUT I LIKE BOYS,
AND I LIKE SEX.

315
00:14:43,832 --> 00:14:45,432
SO DID I, BUT --

316
00:14:45,465 --> 00:14:47,133
"SO DID I"?

317
00:14:47,166 --> 00:14:49,799
[ LAUGHS ]
WAIT A MINUTE.

318
00:14:49,832 --> 00:14:51,832
YOU HAVE A VIRGINITY CLUB,

319
00:14:51,866 --> 00:14:53,799
AND YOU'RE NOT EVEN
A VIRGIN?

320
00:14:53,832 --> 00:14:57,199
I AM NOW.
I'M A BORN-AGAIN VIRGIN.

321
00:14:57,233 --> 00:14:58,233
A WHAT?

322
00:14:58,265 --> 00:14:59,866
JUST BECAUSE
YOU MAKE A MISTAKE

323
00:14:59,899 --> 00:15:01,599
DOESN'T MEAN
YOU CAN'T START OVER.

324
00:15:01,632 --> 00:15:03,699
I MADE A PLEDGE.
I RECOMMITTED.

325
00:15:03,732 --> 00:15:05,732
SHELLY, I HATE
TO BREAK IT TO YOU,

326
00:15:05,766 --> 00:15:08,099
BUT YOU'RE EITHER A VIRGIN
OR YOU'RE NOT,

327
00:15:08,133 --> 00:15:11,233
AND A PLEDGE DOES NOT
A BROKEN HYMEN MEND.

328
00:15:11,265 --> 00:15:12,565
SORRY.

329
00:15:12,599 --> 00:15:14,398
YOU CAN'T TELL ME
WHAT I BELIEVE.

330
00:15:14,432 --> 00:15:15,665
I AM A VIRGIN.

331
00:15:15,699 --> 00:15:17,032
YOU'RE A HYPOCRITE.

332
00:15:17,066 --> 00:15:19,966
YOU ARE WALKING AROUND HERE
PREACHING CELIBACY TO EVERYBODY,

333
00:15:19,999 --> 00:15:22,133
AND YOU'VE ALREADY
SOLD YOUR COW

334
00:15:22,166 --> 00:15:23,966
OR YOUR MILK OR WHATEVER.

335
00:15:23,999 --> 00:15:26,665
WELL, AT LEAST I'M NOT
A BABY KILLER.

336
00:15:26,699 --> 00:15:28,565
I...

337
00:15:28,599 --> 00:15:31,066
UGH!

338
00:15:31,699 --> 00:15:33,166
I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE

339
00:15:33,199 --> 00:15:35,899
I GOT LUPE FIASCO
TO PLAY TRIC TONIGHT.

340
00:15:35,932 --> 00:15:37,398
IT'S GONNA BE AWESOME.

341
00:15:37,432 --> 00:15:40,332
YEAH, IT'S GREAT.
HEY, COOL JACKET.

342
00:15:40,365 --> 00:15:42,866
THANKS.
ELLIE GAVE IT TO ME.

343
00:15:42,899 --> 00:15:46,332
WISH I COULD HAVE MET HER.

344
00:15:46,365 --> 00:15:48,499
IT WAS TOUGH TO TRUST
AT FIRST --

345
00:15:48,532 --> 00:15:51,665
YOU KNOW, HAVING SOMEBODY OUT
THERE THAT YOU'RE RELATED TO.

346
00:15:51,699 --> 00:15:53,298
LIKE YOUR LONG-LOST
BROTHER?

347
00:15:53,332 --> 00:15:54,632
[ CHUCKLES ] YEAH.

348
00:15:54,665 --> 00:15:56,199
[ SIGHS ]

349
00:15:56,233 --> 00:15:58,632
SO, DID IT HURT
WHEN YOU GOT SHOT?

350
00:15:58,665 --> 00:16:00,332
OH, MY GOD -- SO BAD.

351
00:16:00,365 --> 00:16:02,665
YOU GOT A SCAR?
YEAH.

352
00:16:02,699 --> 00:16:03,966
OH, IS IT GROSS?

353
00:16:03,999 --> 00:16:05,265
YES.

354
00:16:05,298 --> 00:16:06,766
OOH, LET ME SEE.
NO!

355
00:16:06,799 --> 00:16:08,632
COME ON.
I'VE NEVER SEEN A GUNSHOT WOUND.

356
00:16:08,665 --> 00:16:09,866
ESPECIALLY IF IT'S GROSS.

357
00:16:09,899 --> 00:16:10,966
COME ON.

358
00:16:11,966 --> 00:16:14,166
FINE.

359
00:16:17,233 --> 00:16:19,166
OH, THAT IS SO SWEET.

360
00:16:19,199 --> 00:16:21,032
WHAT?

361
00:16:21,066 --> 00:16:22,699
JUST BE STILL.

362
00:16:22,732 --> 00:16:25,398
YOU'RE INSANE.
YOU KNOW THAT?

363
00:16:25,432 --> 00:16:28,133
IF THIS ENDS UP ON THE WEB,
I'M COMING AFTER YOU.

364
00:16:28,166 --> 00:16:30,599
TELL YOU WHAT.

365
00:16:30,632 --> 00:16:32,133
FAMILY PHOTO.

366
00:16:35,632 --> 00:16:36,832
READY?

367
00:16:36,866 --> 00:16:38,032
CHEESE!

368
00:16:38,066 --> 00:16:39,499
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

369
00:16:39,532 --> 00:16:42,398
[ Chuckling ] YEAH.

370
00:16:42,432 --> 00:16:44,732
IF YOU'RE HAVING
AN INTERVENTION,

371
00:16:44,766 --> 00:16:47,398
YOU CAN HAVE
MY HEART PILLS.

372
00:16:47,432 --> 00:16:49,999
UM, I ASKED WHITEY
OVER HERE

373
00:16:50,032 --> 00:16:53,866
TO TALK ABOUT YOUR PLAYING
WITH THE RAVENS.

374
00:16:53,899 --> 00:16:56,032
Whitey: YOUR MOM WANTS YOU
BACK ON THE TEAM.

375
00:16:56,066 --> 00:16:57,051
SO DO I.

376
00:16:57,052 --> 00:16:59,052
AND I TALKED
TO THE DOCTOR THIS MORNING,

377
00:16:59,085 --> 00:17:02,319
AND THERE ARE SOME RISKS,
BUT IT'S MANAGEABLE.

378
00:17:02,352 --> 00:17:03,685
SIT DOWN.

379
00:17:03,718 --> 00:17:05,152
WELL...

380
00:17:05,185 --> 00:17:06,818
[ CHUCKLES ]

381
00:17:06,852 --> 00:17:09,085
THERE ARE TWO CONDITIONS.

382
00:17:09,119 --> 00:17:11,319
YOU HAVE TO STAY
ON YOUR MEDICATION,

383
00:17:11,352 --> 00:17:14,119
AND WE LIMIT YOU
TO 15 MINUTES A NIGHT.

384
00:17:14,152 --> 00:17:16,651
I'LL BE BRINGING YOU IN
OFF THE BENCH,

385
00:17:16,685 --> 00:17:19,618
BUT YOU KNOW THAT BENCHES
WIN CHAMPIONSHIPS.

386
00:17:19,651 --> 00:17:23,551
LOOK, I KNOW IT'S DIFFERENT
THAN LAST TIME.

387
00:17:23,585 --> 00:17:25,651
BUT YOU'LL GET TO PLAY.

388
00:17:25,685 --> 00:17:27,551
I...

389
00:17:29,252 --> 00:17:30,718
NO.

390
00:17:30,752 --> 00:17:32,486
LOOK, MOM,

391
00:17:32,518 --> 00:17:36,185
I APPRECIATE EVERYTHING
YOU'RE TRYING TO DO FOR ME,

392
00:17:36,219 --> 00:17:38,718
AND I MISS BASKETBALL
EVERY DAY,

393
00:17:38,752 --> 00:17:42,219
BUT TO HAVE IT HALFWAY,

394
00:17:43,646 --> 00:17:46,746
IT'S HARDER THAN
NOT HAVING IT AT ALL.

395
00:17:53,579 --> 00:17:55,222
SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK?

396
00:17:55,223 --> 00:17:57,023
I GUESS
I'M SUPPOSED TO TELL YOU

397
00:17:57,056 --> 00:17:59,156
YOU HAVE TOO MUCH MAKEUP ON,
YOUR SKIRT'S TOO SHORT,

398
00:17:59,190 --> 00:18:00,824
AND THE BOYS ARE ONLY
OUT FOR ONE THING,

399
00:18:00,857 --> 00:18:03,724
BUT...YOU LOOK BEAUTIFUL.

400
00:18:05,557 --> 00:18:07,290
THANK YOU, PEYTON...

401
00:18:07,323 --> 00:18:09,991
FOR LETTING ME IN,
FOR TRUSTING ME.

402
00:18:10,023 --> 00:18:11,524
IT'S BEEN GREAT.

403
00:18:11,557 --> 00:18:14,390
WELL, THEN IT'S
ABOUT TO GET BETTER

404
00:18:14,423 --> 00:18:17,056
'CAUSE THIS IS SOMETHING
I HAVEN'T TOLD ANYONE.

405
00:18:17,090 --> 00:18:18,724
[ SIGHS ]

406
00:18:18,757 --> 00:18:20,891
LUCAS AND BROOKE
ARE DONE,

407
00:18:20,924 --> 00:18:25,190
SO I'VE DECIDED I'M GOING TO
TELL HIM HOW I FEEL...

408
00:18:25,223 --> 00:18:27,490
TONIGHT.

409
00:18:44,790 --> 00:18:47,156
HUH.
[ SNIFFS ]

410
00:18:57,906 --> 00:18:59,272
HEY.

411
00:18:59,305 --> 00:19:01,672
PLEASE TELL ME WE'RE GOING HOME
ON FOUR WHEELS.

412
00:19:01,706 --> 00:19:03,405
THE GUY WOULDN'T
GIVE ME THE CAR BACK

413
00:19:03,439 --> 00:19:05,106
BECAUSE THE MOTORCYCLE'S
TOO MESSED UP.

414
00:19:05,140 --> 00:19:07,339
BUT LOOK, I'LL FIGURE
SOMETHING OUT, OKAY?

415
00:19:07,372 --> 00:19:09,272
IT JUST MIGHT TAKE ME
A COUPLE OF DAYS.

416
00:19:09,305 --> 00:19:10,639
OKAY.

417
00:19:10,672 --> 00:19:12,973
I'M GOING TO GET A DRINK.

418
00:19:13,006 --> 00:19:15,039
OKAY, JUST THINK
ABOUT IT THIS WAY.

419
00:19:15,073 --> 00:19:16,773
MOST GUYS BUY A MOTORCYCLE

420
00:19:16,806 --> 00:19:18,741
BECAUSE THEY'RE
COMPENSATING FOR...YOU KNOW.

421
00:19:18,742 --> 00:19:20,509
NATHAN WEARS SIZE 14s.

422
00:19:20,543 --> 00:19:23,476
OH, THANKS.
I FEEL SO MUCH BETTER NOW.

423
00:19:27,575 --> 00:19:30,076
CARE TO MAKE
THE NIGHT INTERESTING?

424
00:19:30,109 --> 00:19:31,443
[ CHUCKLES ]

425
00:19:31,476 --> 00:19:34,476
AFTER THE DAY I'VE HAD,
YEAH, SURE.

426
00:19:34,509 --> 00:19:37,608
I'VE GOT SOMETHING FOR YOU,
TOO, BY THE WAY.

427
00:19:37,642 --> 00:19:40,209
UM...

428
00:19:40,242 --> 00:19:44,775
SOMEHOW...THIS ENDED UP
IN MY LOCKER.

429
00:19:44,809 --> 00:19:46,675
HOMETOWN HOTTIE, RIGHT?

430
00:19:46,708 --> 00:19:48,543
HOW WAS THE SHOOT?

431
00:19:48,575 --> 00:19:50,309
WELL, YOU KNOW,

432
00:19:50,342 --> 00:19:53,076
I COULD LET YOU PREVIEW
THE WHOLE SPREAD.

433
00:19:53,109 --> 00:19:55,642
[ CHUCKLES ]

434
00:19:55,675 --> 00:19:57,708
THANKS FOR THE DRINK.

435
00:19:57,742 --> 00:20:00,176
NATHAN, WAIT.

436
00:20:04,575 --> 00:20:06,708
WHAT DID YOU SEE
IN THE WATER?

437
00:20:08,242 --> 00:20:10,376
YOU SAW SOMETHING,
DIDN'T YOU?

438
00:20:10,409 --> 00:20:11,742
WHY WOULD YOU SAY THAT?

439
00:20:11,775 --> 00:20:14,809
NEVER MIND.

440
00:20:24,242 --> 00:20:26,409
Woman: DAN, I ASKED YOU

441
00:20:26,443 --> 00:20:29,176
WHEN YOUR RELATIONSHIP
WITH KEITH CHANGED.

442
00:20:29,209 --> 00:20:30,742
I WAS AWAY AT SCHOOL

443
00:20:30,775 --> 00:20:33,909
WHEN I GOT THE CALL
KAREN WAS IN LABOR.

444
00:20:33,942 --> 00:20:37,608
I DROVE ALL NIGHT LONG
TO BE AT THE HOSPITAL.

445
00:20:37,642 --> 00:20:41,209
BUT SHE NEVER KNEW
I WAS THERE.

446
00:20:41,242 --> 00:20:42,842
WHY NOT?

447
00:20:42,875 --> 00:20:46,409
I ONLY GOT
AS FAR AS THE DOOR.

448
00:20:46,443 --> 00:20:48,509
WHAT DID YOU SEE?

449
00:20:50,142 --> 00:20:55,309
KEITH AT KAREN'S BEDSIDE,
HOLDING MY SON.

450
00:20:55,342 --> 00:20:57,642
HOW YOU DOING, SON?

451
00:20:57,675 --> 00:20:59,975
[ SCOFFS ]
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

452
00:21:00,009 --> 00:21:02,242
SINCE THE LAST TIME
YOU WERE HERE

453
00:21:02,276 --> 00:21:04,376
AND YOU THREATENED
TO KILL ME?

454
00:21:04,409 --> 00:21:07,376
YEAH.
SORRY ABOUT THAT.

455
00:21:07,409 --> 00:21:09,942
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

456
00:21:09,975 --> 00:21:13,109
I EVER TELL YOU
ABOUT MY FINAL GAME?

457
00:21:13,142 --> 00:21:15,909
'87 AGAINST WAKE FOREST.

458
00:21:15,942 --> 00:21:18,742
I WAS ONE REBOUND SHY
OF A DOUBLE-DOUBLE.

459
00:21:18,775 --> 00:21:21,109
AND THEN THERE IT WAS
RIGHT ON THE FRONT OF THE RIM,

460
00:21:21,142 --> 00:21:24,276
AND I JUMPED UP FOR THE BALL
AND CAME DOWN ON MY KNEE.

461
00:21:24,309 --> 00:21:26,742
RIGHT THEN,
I KNEW IT WAS OVER.

462
00:21:26,775 --> 00:21:28,342
I COULD HAVE REHABBED,

463
00:21:28,376 --> 00:21:30,975
BUT I DECIDED
IF I COULDN'T BE THE BEST,

464
00:21:31,009 --> 00:21:33,509
I DIDN'T WANT TO PLAY
THE GAME AT ALL.

465
00:21:33,543 --> 00:21:35,242
I WAS WRONG.

466
00:21:35,276 --> 00:21:38,042
I'D GIVE ANYTHING
TO JUST BE BACK OUT ON THE COURT

467
00:21:38,076 --> 00:21:39,642
FOR 15 MINUTES A NIGHT.

468
00:21:39,675 --> 00:21:40,942
